16: You can't run from me forever...
23:
Dang it! I forgot to pick up some
pepper!
25:
Sorry! You guys go on ahead, I'll be
right—
38:
N-no no, I ran into you... I should be
the one apologizing!
43:
Why are you in such a hurry? ...Are
you being pursued by someone?
55:
Hold on. At least let us take you
somewhere safe.
60:
N-no, I'm fine... I couldn't possibly
bother you like that—
64:
It's no bother here! I was just on my
way to buy some pepper anyways!
77: My name is... Vivi. Nice to meet you.
81:
Nice to meet you... too? Is it just me
or is it getting hot in here?
85:
No need to be so bashful, Alk. She's
no doubt been through a lot. The
least we can do is lend her a
hand—or a back, in this case.
89:
Tell me, Vivi, do you happen to know
the identity of your pursuer?
98:
An assassin?! How did you get
mixed up with someone like that?
108:
My apologies. You must have had
quite the fright. I won't press the
topic any further.
112:
Thank you for understanding...
It's strange, isn't it?
115:
I'm just an ordinary adventurer... I
wonder why he decided to target
me? I'm terrified...
120:
I-I see... Eeeck! W-why are you
touching my back?!
125:
I'm sorry... I get so nervous whenever
I'm around people... Backs are the
only place where I can relax...
133:
So, about this assassin... What was
he like?
138:
...I don't even know his name. He just
started targeting me out of
nowhere...
141: But there is one thing I do know...
150:
Impressive... You truly are a worthy
disciple.
152:
I don't know what you're talking
about...
155:
...Why didn't you take the chance to
kill me? You could have done it
when you snuck up behind me.
158:
I'm not like you! I-I'm just an
adventurer!
163:
...Sooner or later, you'll come to
realize your true destiny. Mark my
words.
169:
You were recruited?! By that
assassin?!
173:
Yes... He kept saying that I had
talent... He was insistent on me
following in his footsteps...
175:
It's true that I have a knack for
sneaking up behind people... And I
do get the occasional urge to press
a pointy object into someone's
back...
179:
But I wouldn't really do that! I just... I
just want to be a normal adventurer!
185:
Then how about joining up with us,
adventurer? We know just the place
for you to hide.
190:
That's right! I doubt that the
assassin could chase you through
the World Flipper!
193:
Are you sure? I couldn't possibly
trouble you any further...
196:
It's no trouble whatsoever. Besides,
your safety is what matters the
most.
200: As long as it's ok with you, of course!
210:
I don't know what to say... Thank
you... Thank you so much!
213:
...In return, I'll be sure to watch your
backs! Hehe.
217: Is it just me or is it getting hot again?!
